text: With no background and pure intention of picking up a new sport, the first trial lesson with Akash went well. Very encouraging for a first timer and time pass super quickly. Would be signing up for more lessons ^^

Aidil is a nice coach. He can immediately find my weak points and provide very useful advise and training. His teaching is encouraging, simple to understand and easy to follow. I learned a lot from just 1 hour session.
The coaches here are friendly and patient. Very good for beginners like me. I went for the trial session and signed up for classes. I have been motivated to go for my trainings every week!

I have played a bit of tennis but it was great to finally get my first lesson from a coach. Eugene was patient and helped my with my form, movement and shot execution. Despite bad weather, I got a lot out of the session and will sign up for more lessons!

A good environment to pick up tennis as a beginner! My coach made the lesson super fun while teaching me the right techniques and was also very attentive so he could give me feedback on my posture etc. Would recommend! :)
